name: TubeCube (Leevi2000)
description:
This is a game I made in Brackeys game jam 2022_1. Also my first finished game project. 
Unfortunately this does not relate to the theme of the jam that much. Maybe I'll be more skilled next time. 

Note: There is a bug where sounds stop after the pace increases. I couldn't fix it easily enough.  

---------------------

Here's a link to the github repo of this game. You can use the sounds in  your projects if you want to, they are made by me. However, I wouldn't recommend copying the code, since it is poorly made in a hurry.
